<h1>Junior Music Course</h1>

No matter what direction your child may take in the future, the musical skills developed in the Yamaha Junior Music Course are a foundation they will cherish for life.

Through the nurturing care of a teacher who loves music, the children will learn the fundamentals of strong keyboard playing skills, aural ability and creativity… but they’ll just think it’s fun

<h2>Curriculum</h2>

<p>
	<strong>Keyboard Performance</strong> – The children learn a wide variety of pieces which develops this<br/>
	<strong>Aural Training</strong> – This is the ideal age<br/>
	<strong>Singing</strong><br/>
	<strong>Music Appreciation</strong><br/>
	<strong>Reading</strong> – Each textbook is accompanied by a workbook which develops the children’s reading and writing skills

<h2>Course Structure</h2>

<p>
	<strong>Lesson duration:</strong> 1 hour per week during school terms<br/>
	<strong>Course duration:</strong> Two years<br/>
	<strong>Class size:</strong> 6-12 students
</p>

